      "writtenOn": "2026-03-26T09:38:56Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The check (rc \u003d\u003d 0 || rc \u003d\u003d 1) is intentional and reflects two different successful outcomes:\n- rc \u003d\u003d 0 means the entry was deleted successfully (only the target file or directory was removed).\n- rc \u003d\u003d 1 means the entry was deleted successfully and, in addition, at least one empty parent directory was also removed.\n\n\n\nIf the deletion fails (rc \u003d\u003d -1), only the error message is printed",
      "parentUuid": "426cd81b_fe3c0f01",
